Mail Server
config is at.
sudo nano /etc/postfix/main.cf
sudo service postfix restart

aliases are in
sudo nano /etc/postfix/virtual
sudo postmap /etc/postfix/virtual

Postfix logs
tail -f -n100 /var/log/maillog

Could add spamassassin?
/etc/init.d/spamassassin start